    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> medium egg noodles</strong> to a pot and cover them with <strong>boiled water</strong> until fully submerged</p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 5-6 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain and reserve a cup of the <strong>starchy noodle water</strong></p>",
